				<td colspan="2"><span>Dermei is correct, but I thought I'd be more specific.
<br />

<br />
Once your brass modifier goes above 2.3 or 2.4 (I can't remember which), you stop getting mitigation messages.  The mobs are still mitigating your slow but you won't see it.  Puretone is a 2.8 mod, so that's why you stopped getting the mitigation messages when Puretone was active.  If you use epic and have Instrument Mastery 3, you'll have to remove your epic to see the mitigation messages.
<br />

<br />
Calli
